| -----------------------------------------  | ---------------------------------- | --------------------------|
|  virtual bool ShouldRun()                          | void registerShouldRunOptionalPassCallback(CallableT) <br> // CallableT = bool(StringRef, Any), called in llvm::PassInstrumentation | |
